observationText: The SK-MEL-153 cell line was used as a target in cytotoxicity assays with effector T-cell clones, indicating it can be cultured and used experimentally.
The SK-MEL-153 cell line was found to express the HLA class I alleles A2, Bw4, and Bw6 based on analysis of its shared phenotype with the SK-MEL-29 cell line.
